1
00:00:52,580 --> 00:00:54,099
[In the Fengwu era,]

2
00:00:54,099 --> 00:00:55,419
[supernatural cases frequently occurred.]

3
00:00:55,459 --> 00:00:57,820
[People lived in constant fear.]

4
00:00:58,739 --> 00:01:00,659
[Demon hunters flourished.]

5
00:01:00,980 --> 00:01:02,379
[To survive, lesser demons]

6
00:01:02,379 --> 00:01:06,059
[often possessed humans to hide their true forms.]

7
00:01:06,299 --> 00:01:09,059
[Only dream-eating demons have no true form.]

8
00:01:09,900 --> 00:01:14,100
[They use Crystal Dream Cup to enter dreams.]

9
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:18,419
[No evil deed goes unnoticed.]

10
00:01:18,699 --> 00:01:21,339
[Good and evil will be rewarded in the end.]

11
00:01:21,820 --> 00:01:24,980
[Today, there's nowhere to escape death.]

12
00:01:25,059 --> 00:01:26,219
[Those who are possessed]

13
00:01:26,219 --> 00:01:28,059
[take their own lives.]

14
00:01:28,740 --> 00:01:33,260
[It survives by devouring nightmares of the most evil.]

15
00:01:34,460 --> 00:01:35,859
[To protect the peace,]

16
00:01:35,859 --> 00:01:36,900
[Prince Shen Que]

17
00:01:36,900 --> 00:01:40,499
[and Qingdu Temple disciples hunt down all evil spirits.]

18
00:01:40,820 --> 00:01:41,980
[With murders on the rise,]

19
00:01:42,299 --> 00:01:45,100
[the people invited a famous Nuo Opera troupe for a ritual.]

20
00:01:46,499 --> 00:01:48,660
[The son of the Vice Minister of Revenue is missing.]

21
00:01:48,660 --> 00:01:49,339
[It's said]

22
00:01:49,980 --> 00:01:51,499
[he's connected to the Nuo Opera troupe.]

23
00:02:10,660 --> 00:02:12,179
[There's a demon!]

24
00:02:12,179 --> 00:02:15,739
[Run!]

25
00:02:16,940 --> 00:02:18,820
[Murder!]

26
00:03:20,299 --> 00:03:21,220
Daozhi...

27
00:03:27,540 --> 00:03:28,540
[Shen Daozhi,]

28
00:03:31,780 --> 00:03:33,380
[I've never experienced this.]

29
00:03:34,220 --> 00:03:35,299
[Why do these images]

30
00:03:35,940 --> 00:03:37,139
[appear before me?]

31
00:03:37,500 --> 00:03:38,699
Shen Daozhi,

32
00:03:39,380 --> 00:03:40,660
we haven't met in a century.

33
00:03:41,139 --> 00:03:42,780
New and old grudges

34
00:03:43,579 --> 00:03:45,299
start settling today.

35
00:03:49,940 --> 00:03:51,060
What demon dares

36
00:03:51,660 --> 00:03:53,500
to act so audaciously before me?

37
00:03:55,060 --> 00:03:55,859
I...

38
00:03:57,419 --> 00:03:58,739
I'm not a demon.

39
00:04:02,060 --> 00:04:02,899
Your Highness,

40
00:04:03,179 --> 00:04:05,780
the missing son of the Vice Minister of Revenue has been found dead.

41
00:04:06,139 --> 00:04:07,820
His body was found in the back yard of the Nuo Opera Troupe.

42
00:04:29,020 --> 00:04:32,379
His death resembles that of my brother.

43
00:04:39,980 --> 00:04:41,660
He killed innocent people.

44
00:04:42,379 --> 00:04:43,900
The evidence is irrefutable.

45
00:04:44,819 --> 00:04:45,619
Demon,

46
00:04:46,299 --> 00:04:47,939
show yourself now!

47
00:04:48,419 --> 00:04:49,739
I didn't kill him.

48
00:04:50,619 --> 00:04:52,059
Please, Your Highness, see the truth.

49
00:04:54,619 --> 00:04:55,859
This body

50
00:04:56,700 --> 00:04:58,140
is indeed well-made.

51
00:04:59,819 --> 00:05:00,819
No wonder you can't let it go.

52
00:05:02,660 --> 00:05:05,540
Your Highness, is this how you treat innocent civilians?

53
00:05:10,780 --> 00:05:11,580
Senior Mu,

54
00:05:12,100 --> 00:05:14,299
can you demonstrate the Five Elements Life-Death Formation

55
00:05:14,819 --> 00:05:15,939
you mentioned before?

56
00:05:16,540 --> 00:05:17,739
Show me.

57
00:05:17,980 --> 00:05:19,299
This formation is extremely cruel.

58
00:05:19,299 --> 00:05:21,859
Both demons and humans will suffer unbearable agony.

59
00:05:21,859 --> 00:05:23,220
If this woman is not a demon,

60
00:05:23,220 --> 00:05:25,259
she probably can't withstand such purification.

61
00:05:25,259 --> 00:05:25,939
Set the array.

62
00:05:28,939 --> 00:05:29,460
Yes.

63
00:05:30,980 --> 00:05:31,660
Set the array.

64
00:05:37,379 --> 00:05:38,140
The Five Elements start and stop.

65
00:05:38,140 --> 00:05:39,220
Life and death are sealed and imprisoned.

66
00:05:39,340 --> 00:05:39,939
Clear.

67
00:06:09,819 --> 00:06:10,540
Your Highness,

68
00:06:10,700 --> 00:06:12,299
no demons appeared in the array.

69
00:06:12,299 --> 00:06:13,540
This woman is not a demon.

70
00:06:16,220 --> 00:06:16,939
Take her back.

71
00:06:18,059 --> 00:06:19,179
Lock her in the dungeon.

72
00:06:19,179 --> 00:06:19,980
Yes.

73
00:06:29,540 --> 00:06:31,340
[Torture won't reveal the truth,]

74
00:06:32,379 --> 00:06:38,020
[and the truth will be hard to uncover.]

75
00:07:01,900 --> 00:07:04,939
[The Prince Xian is indeed as cruel as they say.]

76
00:07:05,780 --> 00:07:07,179
[In that case,]

77
00:07:07,460 --> 00:07:10,020
[I should let him experience]

78
00:07:11,819 --> 00:07:14,259
[the agony of being pierced by arrows.]

79
00:08:20,179 --> 00:08:21,739
Your Highness.

80
00:08:24,460 --> 00:08:26,379
Your Highness.

81
00:08:28,059 --> 00:08:29,499
Shen Que.

82
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:34,139
Your Highness.

83
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:46,100
As you wish,

84
00:08:52,460 --> 00:08:53,859
I am indeed a demon.

85
00:09:21,779 --> 00:09:23,300
Your Highness,

86
00:09:23,700 --> 00:09:25,259
you are indeed quite beautiful.

87
00:09:26,060 --> 00:09:27,940
What kind of demon are you?

88
00:09:28,420 --> 00:09:29,300
Don't worry,

89
00:09:30,460 --> 00:09:31,739
you'll remember soon enough.

90
00:10:05,899 --> 00:10:07,739
[This woman must be a demon.]

91
00:10:25,739 --> 00:10:26,539
Luo'an,

92
00:10:26,820 --> 00:10:27,779
is Shen Que

93
00:10:27,980 --> 00:10:30,060
the reincarnation of Shen Daozhi, who took your spiritual root?

94
00:10:35,019 --> 00:10:36,779
Have you found the location of the spiritual root in his dreams?

95
00:10:36,779 --> 00:10:38,019
He is very cautious.

96
00:10:38,460 --> 00:10:39,580
In the shallow dream realm,

97
00:10:39,859 --> 00:10:41,379
[only his current life's experiences.]

98
00:10:42,139 --> 00:10:44,180
[I need to find the gate to the deep dream.]

99
00:10:44,940 --> 00:10:46,820
[I must make him fall for me quickly,]

100
00:10:47,259 --> 00:10:48,259
[or I'll never]

101
00:10:49,100 --> 00:10:50,820
[reach his deep dream.]

102
00:10:50,820 --> 00:10:51,379
[Li,]

103
00:10:51,739 --> 00:10:53,300
[don't fall for him again.]

104
00:10:55,259 --> 00:10:56,379
[Impossible.]

105
00:10:59,739 --> 00:11:01,460
[In my past life, he took advantage of my youth,]

106
00:11:03,980 --> 00:11:05,379
[using sweet talk]

107
00:11:06,659 --> 00:11:08,379
[to win my heart,]

108
00:11:08,940 --> 00:11:11,180
[then struck when I was most vulnerable,]

109
00:11:11,940 --> 00:11:14,859
[when I was most vulnerable.]

110
00:11:15,060 --> 00:11:16,940
[If he hadn't stolen my Spiritual Root,]

111
00:11:17,300 --> 00:11:18,779
[and left me in a hundred-year slumber,]

112
00:11:19,100 --> 00:11:22,340
[the Demon Clan wouldn't have been reduced]

113
00:11:22,340 --> 00:11:24,779
[to hiding in remote villages.]

114
00:11:25,859 --> 00:11:27,300
[With my Spiritual Root back,]

115
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:30,340
[I'll have the power to protect the clan.]

116
00:11:41,940 --> 00:11:43,300
[Once I take back my Spiritual Root]

117
00:11:43,340 --> 00:11:44,300
[and restore my Demon Power,]

118
00:11:44,460 --> 00:11:45,460
[I'll make him,]

119
00:11:45,700 --> 00:11:47,899
[and all those demon hunters,]

120
00:11:49,779 --> 00:11:50,899
[pay for their crimes.]

121
00:11:52,180 --> 00:11:53,220
with blood!

122
00:11:54,619 --> 00:11:55,619
Your Highness.
